{"type":"message","id":"3de48e00","parentId":"e43f69f9","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:50:19.064Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The email sending failed because the SMTP configuration is missing. I recommend configuring the following settings in `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`:\n\n- **EMAIL_SMTP_SERVER** (e.g., `smtp.gmail.com`)\n- **EMAIL_SMTP_PORT** (465 for SSL or 587 for TLS)\n- **EMAIL_SENDER** (the sender email address)\n- **EMAIL_SMTP_PASSWORD** (authorization code or app password)\n\nOnce these settings are added, I can attempt to send the email again. Would you like help setting this up?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"github-copilot","model":"gpt-4o","usage":{"input":162,"output":114,"cacheRead":17408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17684,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775814615510,"responseId":"chatcmpl-DT2nBrzOPcteqVB4HxNQfWKba9GJI"}}
